[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 06:18, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}}
{{afc comment|1=I used to be confident this was an independent deity. But apparently I got her gender wrong. I think she is actually identical to or an epithet of [[Tamayori-hime_(mother_of_Jimmu)|Tamayori-hime]] and bore {{ill|Takeuioki-no-Mikoto|ja|武位起命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeuioki-no-Mikoto|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} with [[Hoori]] when [[Ugayafukiaezu]] was still a child.[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 14:42, 14 May 2025 (UTC)}}

